ACADEMIC ORIGIN
RetinaGuard is the extended development of a diabetic retinopathy detection system
originally conceived and built jointly by Gaurav Singh Thakur and Niharika Raghunandan
as part of their undergraduate research. This platform represents the continued
evolution of that shared academic work into a full-stack clinical screening application.

By accessing, viewing, cloning, forking, downloading, or otherwise obtaining any
portion of this Software, you agree to be bound by the terms of this License.
If you do not agree to these terms, you must immediately delete all copies of the
Software in your possession.

